<ab facs="#facs_7_r1l6">des Juden <expan>Hohmeıſt<ex>er</ex>s</expan> vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> perſon daſelbs bey eẅch / den Juden <expan>hohmeıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_7_r1l7">von der <expan>ſecklin<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> . vnd dıe <expan>vorgen<ex>ante</ex></expan> ſache gen der golden genſin ʒum </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_7_r1l8"> <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> auf Jn <expan>gebotte<ex>n</ex></expan> . vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough">wölt all </del> erbutt ſıch <expan>all<ex>e</ex>m</expan> dem <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gnug ʒutun daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_7_r1l9">von <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> auf den <expan>freıt<ex>ag</ex></expan> vor dem ſunntag <expan>Jnuocau<ex>i</ex><hi rend="sup">t</hi></expan> nehſtuer = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_7_r1l10"><expan>gang<ex>en</ex></expan> / <expan>ʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>beıde<ex>n</ex></expan> teıln bey vns beredt <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> Vnd des hab er von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_7_r1l11"><expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>meıſt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ein geſchrıbne ʒeẅknuſſ von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd be = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_7_r1l12">gert / dıe Jm niht <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> möcht vnd doch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> <expan>ſtepf<ex>an</ex></expan> <expan>ſchreıb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
